                vendors, suppliers and customers. Comply with all applicable
                laws and regulations while processing, transmitting, or storing
                personal data. Ensure that all data is protected. In the event
                of any improper disclosure or breach of personal or sensitive
                data, notify TCI without delay and as provided by applicable
                contractual and legal requirements. You should also take
                reasonable and legally required steps following such an event.
              </dd>
              <dd class="hero-sub-title-2 mt-5">
                1.7. Intellectual Property and Confidential Information
              </dd>
              <dd class="hero-sub-title" style="padding-left: 3em">
